Subject: [PATCH 2134/2351] drm/meson: venc: add ENCL encoder setup for
 MIPI-DSI output

This adds supports for the ENCL encoder connected to a MIPI-DSI transceiver on the
Amlogic AXG, G12A, G12B & SM1 SoCs.

