Reviewed-by: Nicolas Belin <nbelin@baylibre.com>
Tested-by: Nicolas Belin <nbelin@baylibre.com> # on Khadas VIM3 + TS050 Panel
Signed-off-by: Neil Armstrong <neil.armstrong@linaro.org>
